@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About - TrufadecuTTS</PageTitle>

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                    <h3 class="mb-0">
                        <i class="bi bi-info-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                        About TrufadecuTTS
                    </h3>
                    <small>Google Cloud Text-to-Speech Interface</small>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-8">
                            
                            <!-- Application Description -->
                            <div class="card mb-4">
                                <div class="card-header">
                                    <h5 class="mb-0"><i class="bi bi-app-indicator me-2"></i>Application Overview</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p class="lead">
                                        TrufadecuTTS is a comprehensive interface for Google Cloud Text-to-Speech API 
                                        designed to provide easy access to all TTS features in just 2 clicks.
                                    </p>
                                    
                                    <h6>Key Features:</h6>
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-md-6">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><strong>Selective Interface:</strong> Access all TTS parameters</li>
                                                <li><strong>Voice Selection:</strong> 380+ voices, 50+ languages</li>
                                                <li><strong>Audio Controls:</strong> Rate, pitch, volume adjustments</li>
                                                <li><strong>Format Options:</strong> MP3, WAV, OGG, and more</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-6">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><strong>Quick Presets:</strong> Normal, slow, fast voice settings</li>
                                                <li><strong>Real-time Preview:</strong> Instant parameter feedback</li>
                                                <li><strong>Easy Configuration:</strong> Simple API setup guide</li>
                                                <li><strong>Cross-platform:</strong> Works on any modern browser</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Google Cloud TTS Features -->
                            <div class="card mb-4">
                                <div class="card-header">
                                    <h5 class="mb-0"><i class="bi bi-cloud-fill me-2"></i>Google Cloud Text-to-Speech Features</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-md-4">
                                            <div class="text-center mb-3">
                                                <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" 
                                                     style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-person-voice fs-4"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <h6 class="mt-2">Voice Variety</h6>
                                                <small class="text-muted">
                                                    380+ voices across 50+ languages with natural-sounding speech
                                                </small>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-4">
                                            <div class="text-center mb-3">
                                                <div class="bg-success text-white rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" 
                                                     style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-robot fs-4"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <h6 class="mt-2">Neural Voices</h6>
                                                <small class="text-muted">
                                                    WaveNet and Neural2 voices for ultra-realistic speech synthesis
                                                </small>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-4">
                                            <div class="text-center mb-3">
                                                <div class="bg-info text-white rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" 
                                                     style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-sliders fs-4"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <h6 class="mt-2">Advanced Controls</h6>
                                                <small class="text-muted">
                                                    Fine-tune speaking rate, pitch, volume, and audio profiles
                                                </small>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-md-4">
                                            <div class="text-center mb-3">
                                                <div class="bg-warning text-dark rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" 
                                                     style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-music-note-beamed fs-4"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <h6 class="mt-2">Audio Formats</h6>
                                                <small class="text-muted">
                                                    Multiple audio formats: MP3, WAV, OGG, μ-law, A-law
                                                </small>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-4">
                                            <div class="text-center mb-3">
                                                <div class="bg-secondary text-white rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" 
                                                     style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-stopwatch fs-4"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <h6 class="mt-2">Real-time</h6>
                                                <small class="text-muted">
                                                    Streaming synthesis for real-time applications
                                                </small>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-4">
                                            <div class="text-center mb-3">
                                                <div class="bg-danger text-white rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" 
                                                     style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-shield-check fs-4"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <h6 class="mt-2">Enterprise Ready</h6>
                                                <small class="text-muted">
                                                    Secure, scalable, and compliant with enterprise requirements
                                                </small>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Implementation Guide -->
                            <div class="card">
                                <div class="card-header">
                                    <h5 class="mb-0"><i class="bi bi-code-slash me-2"></i>Implementation Guide</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>
                                        This application provides a complete interface for Google Cloud Text-to-Speech API. 
                                        To enable full functionality, you need to implement a server-side component.
                                    </p>

                                    <div class="alert alert-info">
                                        <h6><i class="bi bi-lightbulb-fill me-2"></i>Why Server-Side Implementation?</h6>
                                        <ul class="mb-0">
                                            <li><strong>Security:</strong> API credentials should never be exposed in client-side code</li>
                                            <li><strong>CORS:</strong> Browser security prevents direct calls to Google Cloud APIs</li>
                                            <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> Service account credentials require server-side handling</li>
                                            <li><strong>Billing Control:</strong> Server-side implementation allows better usage monitoring</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>

                                    <h6>Server Implementation Steps:</h6>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li><strong>Create API Endpoint:</strong> Develop a REST API that accepts TTS requests</li>
                                        <li><strong>Handle Authentication:</strong> Securely manage Google Cloud service account credentials</li>
                                        <li><strong>Process Requests:</strong> Convert UI parameters to Google Cloud TTS API calls</li>
                                        <li><strong>Return Audio:</strong> Send synthesized audio back to the client</li>
                                        <li><strong>Error Handling:</strong> Implement proper error responses and logging</li>
                                    </ol>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

